    <p>GRAHAM: This is totally - listen...</p>
    <p>MARTIN: ...This is another issue in which, you know - that those attitudes have changed.</p>
    <p>GRAHAM: It's totally - this is totally different. This is - this is God's standards. And just because public opinion may have changed or somebody takes a poll - this is just one of the issues. And it doesn't matter what people say or what people think. It doesn't matter about the opinion polls. It's what God says, and God says this is a sin. And it's a sin against him, and he's going to judge sin.</p>
