    <p>UNIDENTIFIED CHILD: Those yours?</p>
    <p>AALTO: The wonderful thing about this game is that there is no strategy. Right, so shall we play?</p>
    <p>SHAPIRO: All right.</p>
    <p>AALTO: All right then.</p>
